error: Class "Your_class" hides a global script class
meaning: A script defined a "class_name" that conflicts with an existing global class.
causes: Using a "class_name" that matches a built-in engine class
Name collision with a plugin or addon class
Stale editor cache referencing a removed class
fixes: Rename the "class_name" to be globally unique
Avoid using names of built-in engine classes
Clear the .godot/ folder and reload the project
